                        <collation>
                           <p>
									Originally 41 quires of 10 leaves.  
									A number of lacunas in the first 4 and the last 10 quires. The first quire is defective. 
									Folios 1-37 contain 4 quires signed with Hebrew letters on the first page; folios 38-307 have 27 quires signed with Hebrew letters on first page; folios 308-410 contain more than 10 quires signed with Hebrew letters on the first and the last page. 
								</p>
